{"type": "article", "id": 30107, "title": "多功能收纳柜", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-25T23:06:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607252151373WgA6YiM2ocjSbms.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>来自俄罗斯的 <a href=\"http://alexanderkanygin.tictail.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alexander Kanygin</a> 利用橡木制作了一款名为 MTO 的收纳系统，乍一看似乎和市面上常见的收纳盒并没有什么太大的差别，但只要做略微的调整你就会发现它不仅仅是个分割出几个空间的收纳工具。实际上它由两个木盒所组成，通过橡皮圈相连。木盒的每一面都被设计了不同的功能，根据需要进行翻转组合后，可以同时用做零钱罐、笔筒、绕线器等等，能够满足人们的日常需求，无论是放在办公室还是家中的玄关处都很合适。这是它的<a href=\"http://alexanderkanygin.tictail.com/product/mto\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 13500 卢布。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725221644V9NCGoFJTvanU0Ep.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725221644dENItODW3whU5zGB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725221645SzcVPs4Y9MR128F3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725221645BsMDm8Utfc9yCNHA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}